BWiener R package
=================
Modelling functions for the Wiener diffusion model, based on Bayesian
Methods (MCMC sampling).

Using the package
-----------------
::

  bwdm(data, yvar=c("q", "resp"), alpha=NULL, tau=NULL, beta=NULL, delta=NULL,
               xvar=NULL, start=NULL, fixed=0, jagscmd=NULL, idvar="id")
  hwdm(data, jagscmd=NULL, model="hwdm", idvar="id", condvar=NULL)

See the R man pages for more details!

